{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"250157bdee","title":"对《毛主席诗词》若干词句的解释","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4921aa35bc","index":0,"year":1964,"month":1,"day":27,"articleId":"250157bdee"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji46","name":"毛泽东全集第46卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/46-OCR.pdf"},{"id":"wenji8","name":"毛泽东文集第八卷（1999）","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"中央文献研究室","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives9/main/books/wenji8.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji46":{"comments":[{"id":"09216d07d8","publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"1963年《毛主席诗词》出版后，外文出版发行事业局组织翻译出版英译本。1964年1月，毛泽东应英译者的请求，就自已诗词中的一些词句作了口头解释。这是英译者对毛泽东的解释所作记录的要点。"},{"id":"7d37110102","publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"参见《沁园春·长沙》。"},{"id":"0049ac5b51","publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"参见《西江月·并冈山》。14]参见《清平乐·蒋桂战争》。"},{"id":"59aeca9528","publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee","index":4,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"参见《蝶恋花·从汀州向长沙》。参见《渔家傲·反第二次大“围”》。参见《清平乐·会昌》。参见《十六字令三首》。"},{"id":"b2b72a212f","publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee","index":5,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"参见《忆秦娥·娄山关》。"},{"id":"fae323588e","publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee","index":6,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"参见《七律·长征》。"},{"id":"d27ca4f586","publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee","index":7,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"参见《七律·人民解放军占领南京》"},{"id":"02a00f522b","publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee","index":8,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"参见《七律·人民解放军占领南京》参见《浪淘沙·北戴河》。参见《蝶恋花·答李淑一》。"},{"id":"35cd0345c8","publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee","index":9,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"参见《七律二首·送温神》。"},{"id":"57c8427269","publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee","index":10,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"参见《七律·到韶山》。"},{"id":"d548f7f1cb","publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee","index":11,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"参见《七律·登庐山》。"},{"id":"f1ca5b6c8d","publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee","index":12,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"参见《七律·答友人》。"},{"id":"5db7937530","publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee","index":13,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"参见《七律·答友人》。"},{"id":"24aac24341","publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee","index":14,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"参见《七律·为李进同志题所摄庐山仙人洞照》。"},{"id":"d0706619c0","publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee","index":15,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"参见《七律·和郭沫若同志》。"},{"id":"bb463c801d","publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee","index":16,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"参见《满江红·和郭沫若同志》。"},{"id":"add4e84098","publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee","index":17,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"参见《满江红·和郭沫若同志》。"}],"contents":[{"id":"177e592f35","type":"title","text":"对《毛主席诗词》若干词句的解释”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"09216d07d8","type":"paragraph","text":"一、“帐零廊，问苍范大地，谁主沉浮？”回","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"7d37110102","type":"paragraph","text":"这句是指：在北伐以前，军阀统治，中国的命运究竟由哪一个阶级做主","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"0049ac5b51","type":"paragraph","text":"二、“到中流击水”以。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"59aeca9528","type":"paragraph","text":"“击水”指在湘江中游泳。当时我写的诗有两句还记得：“自信人生二百年，会当水击三千里。”那时有个因是子（蒋维乔），提借一种静坐法。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"b2b72a212f","type":"paragraph","text":"三、“山下族旗在望，山头鼓角相闻。国","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"fae323588e","type":"paragraph","text":"“旋旗”和“鼓角”都是指我军。黄洋界很陆，阵地在山腰，指挥在山头，敌人仰攻。山下并没有都被敌人占领，没有严重到这个程度。“旋旗在望”，其实没有飘扬的旗子，都是卷起的。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"d27ca4f586","type":"paragraph","text":"四、“一枕黄梁再现”。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"02a00f522b","type":"paragraph","text":"指军阀的黄梁梦。","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"35cd0345c8","type":"paragraph","text":"五、“国际悲歌歌一曲”以","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"57c8427269","type":"paragraph","text":"“悲”是悲壮之意。","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"d548f7f1cb","type":"paragraph","text":"六、“枯木柄株齐努力。枪林逼，飞将军自重雪入。”回","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"f1ca5b6c8d","type":"paragraph","text":"“枯木朽株”，不是指敌方，是指自己这边，草木也可帮我们忙。“枪林逼”也是指自己这边。“枪林逼，飞将军自重雪入”是倒装笔法，就是：“飞将军自重雪入，枪林逼。","index":12,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"5db7937530","type":"subtitle","text":"七、“莫道君行早”以。","index":13,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"24aac24341","type":"paragraph","text":"“君行早”的“君”，指我自己，不是复数，要照单数译。会昌有高山，天不亮我就去爬山。","index":14,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"d0706619c0","type":"subtitle","text":"八、“离天三尺三”。","index":15,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"bb463c801d","type":"paragraph","text":"这是湖南常德的民谣。","index":16,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"add4e84098","type":"paragraph","text":"九、“西风烈，长空雁叫霜晨月。......雄关漫道真如铁，而今迈步从头越。（51","index":17,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"966d4ded21","type":"paragraph","text":"这首词上下两离不是分写两次攻打娄山关，而是写一次。这里北有大巴山，长江、乌江之间也有山脉挡风，所以一二月也不太冷。“雁叫”“霜晨”，是写当时景象。云贵地区就是这样，昆明更是四季如春。遵义会议后，红军北上，准备过长江，但是遇到强大阻力。为了甩开敌军，出敌不意，杀回马枪，红军又回头走，决心回遵义，结果第二次打下了娄山关，重占遵义。过娄山关时，太阳还没有落山。","index":18,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"41e0f6865e","type":"paragraph","text":"十、“五岭透逸腾细浪，乌蒙磅磷走泥丸。","index":19,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"80db2ba753","type":"paragraph","text":"把山比作“细浪”“泥丸”，是“等闲”之意","index":20,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"951912ad92","type":"paragraph","text":"十一、“天若有情天亦老”问。","index":21,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"a16d3e4a0c","type":"paragraph","text":"这是借用季贺的句子。与人间比，大是不老的。其实天也有发生、发展、衰亡。天是自然界，包括有机界，如细菌、动物。自然界、人类社会，一样有发生和灭亡的过程。社会上的阶级，有兴起，有灭亡。","index":22,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"0e7a553bc8","type":"paragraph","text":"十二、“一片汪洋都不见，知向谁边？”以","index":23,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"707ae28511","type":"paragraph","text":"是指渔船不见。","index":24,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"569144e198","type":"paragraph","text":"十三、“泪飞顿作倾盆雨”问。","index":25,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"8adb04f011","type":"paragraph","text":"是指高兴得掉泪。","index":26,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"8777626179","type":"paragraph","text":"十四、“坐地日行八万里，巡天遥看一千河。”回","index":27,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"b0890e210d","type":"paragraph","text":"人坐在地球这颗行星上，不要买票，在宇宙里旅行。地球自转的里数，就是人旅行的里数。地球直径为一万二千七百多公里，乘以圆周率，即赤道长，约四万公里，再折合成华里，约八万里。人在二十四小时内走了八方里","index":28,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"9b6e90a9f6","type":"paragraph","text":"十五、“牛郎欲问遮神事”同","index":29,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"929cfcd616","type":"paragraph","text":"牛郎织女是普朝人的传说","index":30,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"4148b3d319","type":"subtitle","text":"十六、“红雨随心翻作浪，青山着意化为桥。回","index":31,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"6e5dc67e3d","type":"paragraph","text":"“红雨”指桃花。写这句是为下句创造条件。“青山着意化为桥”，指青山穿洞成为桥。这两句诗有水有桥。","index":32,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"e74bd53851","type":"paragraph","text":"十七、“别梦依稀见逝川，故园三十二年前。.....黑手高悬霸主鞭。”1","index":33,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"f954b6fcb0","type":"subtitle","text":"“咒逝川”“三十二年前”，指大革命失败，反动派镇压了革命。","index":34,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"b1f34fbc78","type":"paragraph","text":"这里的“霸主”，就是指蒋介石。","index":35,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"05d4fb43dd","type":"paragraph","text":"十八、“冷眼向洋看世界”以。","index":36,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"9decedf2b9","type":"paragraph","text":"“冷眼向洋”就是“横眉冷对”","index":37,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"5287444965","type":"paragraph","text":"十九、“云横九派浮黄鹤”以。","index":38,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"942842c33e","type":"paragraph","text":"“黄鹤”不是指黄鹤楼。“九派”指这一带的河流，是长江的支流。明朝季攀龙有一首送朋友的诗《怀明卿》：“豫章西望彩云间，九派长江九叠山。高卧不须镜石镜，秋风怪侍臣颜。”李攀龙是“后七子”之一。明朝也有好诗，但《明诗综》不好，《明诗别裁》好。","index":39,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"7afc888dee","type":"paragraph","text":"二十、“浪下三吴起白烟”问。","index":40,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"366955c95b","type":"paragraph","text":"“白烟”为水。","index":41,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"07fdc0f279","type":"subtitle","text":"二十一、“陶今不知何处去，桃花源里可耕田？”问","index":42,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"5e147af5e2","type":"paragraph","text":"陶渊明设想了一个名为桃花源的理想世界，没有租税，没有压追。","index":43,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"451e43c256","type":"paragraph","text":"二十二、《七律·答友人》的“友人”指谁？","index":44,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"5b4cbbdf73","type":"paragraph","text":"“发人”指周世钊。","index":45,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"1fa82bff5a","type":"paragraph","text":"二十三、“九疑山上白云飞”同。","index":46,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"edc35d10a4","type":"paragraph","text":"“九鼻山”，即苍梧山，在湖南省南部。","index":47,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"d1a999f5df","type":"paragraph","text":"二十四、“红霞万朵百重衣”以","index":48,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"4b19f18924","type":"paragraph","text":"“红霞”，指帝子衣服。","index":49,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"b7c278ba91","type":"paragraph","text":"二十五、“洞庭波涌连天雪”","index":50,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"bca8ecd21c","type":"subtitle","text":"下”。“洞庭波”，取自《楚辞》中的《九歌·湘夫人》：“洞庭波分木叶二十六、“长岛人歌动地诗”。","index":51,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"bba27a8d28","type":"paragraph","text":"“长岛”即水陆洲，也叫橘子洲，长沙因此得名，就像汉口因在汉水之口而得名一样。","index":52,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"6ac36eb54c","type":"paragraph","text":"二十七、“芙蓉国里尽朝晖”。","index":53,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"7f1ef06894","type":"paragraph","text":"“芙蓉国”，指湖南，见谭用之诗“秋风方里芙蓉国”。“芙蓉是指木芙蓉，不是水芙蓉，水芙蓉是荷花。谭诗可查《全唐诗》。","index":54,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"b8b5787498","type":"paragraph","text":"二十八、“幕色苍范看劲松，乱云飞渡仍从容。”","index":55,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"5b5e0d1496","type":"paragraph","text":"是云从容，不是松从容。","index":56,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"3aadbf0004","type":"paragraph","text":"二十九、“僧是思氓犹可训，妖为鬼城必成灾。国","index":57,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"94163a76a1","type":"paragraph","text":"郭沫若原诗针对唐借。应针对白骨精。唐僧是不觉悟的人，被欺骗了。我的和诗是驳郭老的。","index":58,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"fe8186b49c","type":"subtitle","text":"三十、“妈蚁缘槐夸大国”问。","index":59,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"4c36c3e5ed","type":"paragraph","text":"大槐安国”是汤显祖《南柯记》里的故事。","index":60,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"2590f2172f","type":"paragraph","text":"三十一、“正西风落叶下长安，飞鸣销。问","index":61,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"816bf3198d","type":"subtitle","text":"“飞鸣”指我们的进攻。“正西风落叶下长安”，虫子怕秋冬。","index":62,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"0a3798be0e","type":"paragraph","text":"形势变得很快，那时是“百文冰”，而现在正是“四海翻腾云水怒，五洲震荡风雷激”了。从去年起，我们进攻，九月开始写文章，一评苏共中央的公开信。","index":63,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"d39ac58d78","type":"subtitle","text":"三十二、“天地转，光阴迫。一万年太久，只争朝夕。三","index":64,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"802a60c5ca","type":"paragraph","text":"你要慢，我就要快，反其道而行之。你想活一万年？没有那么长。我要马上见高低，争个明白，不容许塘塞。但其实时间在我们这边，“只争朝夕”，我们也没有那么急。","index":65,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee"}],"page":{"id":"5e451d13d1","publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"250157bdee","start":216,"end":221}},"wenji8":{"comments":[{"id":"0ced351421","publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee","index":14,"part_index":27,"offset":21,"text":"见《七律二首·送瘟神》。"},{"id":"197c80a4a3","publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee","index":5,"part_index":9,"offset":11,"text":"见《蝶恋花·从汀州向长沙》。"},{"id":"1b85079135","publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee","index":4,"part_index":7,"offset":10,"text":"见《清平乐·蒋桂战争》。"},{"id":"48778bc06b","publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee","index":9,"part_index":17,"offset":34,"text":"见《忆秦娥·娄山关》。"},{"id":"4fcd501c75","publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee","index":11,"part_index":21,"offset":12,"text":"见《七律·人民解放军占领南京》。"},{"id":"5fd0cc06ae","publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee","index":10,"part_index":19,"offset":20,"text":"见《七律·长征》。"},{"id":"73ec3d79d0","publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee","index":2,"part_index":1,"offset":19,"text":"见《沁园春·长沙》。"},{"id":"7a5b23e8d8","publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee","index":6,"part_index":11,"offset":24,"text":"见《渔家傲·反第二次大“围剿”》。"},{"id":"820f0f8636","publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee","index":8,"part_index":15,"offset":9,"text":"见《十六字令三首》。"},{"id":"99b1be858c","publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee","index":7,"part_index":13,"offset":9,"text":"见《清平乐·会昌》。"},{"id":"a188a9a595","publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee","index":15,"part_index":33,"offset":31,"text":"见《七律·到韶山》。"},{"id":"bab7f66333","publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee","index":16,"part_index":35,"offset":12,"text":"见《七律·登庐山》。"},{"id":"bbeefcc806","publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee","index":3,"part_index":5,"offset":18,"text":"见《西江月·井冈山》。"},{"id":"c4b0fdeda1","publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee","index":13,"part_index":25,"offset":12,"text":"见《蝶恋花·答李淑一》。"},{"id":"ca157d4087","publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee","index":19,"part_index":57,"offset":22,"text":"见《七律·和郭沫若同志》。"},{"id":"dc32613c12","publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee","index":12,"part_index":23,"offset":18,"text":"见《浪淘沙·北戴河》。"},{"id":"de9974c0f6","publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee","index":1,"part_index":0,"offset":15,"text":"一九六三年《毛主席诗词》出版后，外文出版发行事业局组织翻译出版英译本。一九六四年一月，毛泽东应英译者的请求，就自己诗词中的一些词句作了口头解释。这是英译者对毛泽东的解释所作记录的要点。"},{"id":"efb0cdf8ae","publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee","index":20,"part_index":59,"offset":12,"text":"见《满江红·和郭沫若同志》。"},{"id":"f627f8e286","publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee","index":17,"part_index":45,"offset":13,"text":"见《七律·答友人》。"},{"id":"f8b8ca0bcd","publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee","index":18,"part_index":55,"offset":22,"text":"见《七绝·为李进同志题所摄庐山仙人洞照》。"}],"contents":[{"id":"000df23e83","type":"paragraph","text":"十八、“冷眼向洋看世界”。","index":35,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"0ced351421","type":"paragraph","text":"“君行早”的“君”，指我自己，不是复数，要照单数译。会昌有高山，天不亮我就去爬山。","index":14,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"0e0dc7dc69","type":"paragraph","text":"“黄鹤”不是指黄鹤楼。“九派”指这一带的河流，是长江的支流。明朝李攀龙有一首送朋友的诗《怀明卿》：“豫章西望彩云间，九派长江九叠山。高卧不须窥石镜，秋风憔悴侍臣颜。”李攀龙是“后七子”之一。明朝也有好诗，但《明诗综》不好，《明诗别裁》好。","index":38,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"197c80a4a3","type":"paragraph","text":"三、“山下旌旗在望，山头鼓角相闻。”","index":5,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"1b85079135","type":"paragraph","text":"“击水”指在湘江中游泳。当时我写的诗有两句还记得：“自信人生二百年，会当水击三千里。”那时有个因是子（蒋维乔），提倡一种静坐法。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"2de7640f8f","type":"paragraph","text":"二十六、“长岛人歌动地诗”。","index":51,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"344339b4ae","type":"title","text":"对《毛主席诗词》若干词句的解释","index":0,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"37cb14a868","type":"paragraph","text":"十九、“云横九派浮黄鹤”。","index":37,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"3a305e4f25","type":"paragraph","text":"“大槐安国”是汤显祖《南柯记》里的故事。","index":60,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"3a9d4ff858","type":"paragraph","text":"二十三、“九嶷山上白云飞”。","index":45,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"3c48d5a28a","type":"paragraph","text":"《毛泽东诗词集》刊印。","index":66,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"3c9f069841","type":"paragraph","text":"牛郎织女是晋朝人的传说。","index":30,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"3fd0db3d9c","type":"paragraph","text":"三十二、“天地转，光阴迫。一万年太久，只争朝夕。”","index":63,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"444e840c3c","type":"paragraph","text":"“红雨”指桃花。写这句是为下句创造条件。“青山着意化为桥”，指青山穿洞成为桥。这两句诗有水有桥。","index":32,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"453922ad67","type":"paragraph","text":"三十、“蚂蚁缘槐夸大国”。","index":59,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"45baabcf30","type":"paragraph","text":"二十五、“洞庭波涌连天雪”。","index":49,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"47336b522b","type":"paragraph","text":"二十七、“芙蓉国里尽朝晖”。","index":53,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"48778bc06b","type":"paragraph","text":"五、“国际悲歌歌一曲”。","index":9,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"4cd543f38c","type":"paragraph","text":"陶渊明设想了一个名为桃花源的理想世界，没有租税，没有压迫。","index":42,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"4fcd501c75","type":"paragraph","text":"六、“枯木朽株齐努力。枪林逼，飞将军自重霄入。”","index":11,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"595b57e7e9","type":"paragraph","text":"二十一、“陶令不知何处去，桃花源里可耕田？”","index":41,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"597c0f507d","type":"paragraph","text":"是云从容，不是松从容。","index":56,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"5fd0cc06ae","type":"paragraph","text":"“悲”是悲壮之意。","index":10,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"669e6d4826","type":"paragraph","text":"是指渔船不见。","index":24,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"6902468cc5","type":"paragraph","text":"你要慢，我就要快，反其道而行之。你想活一万年？没有那么长。我要马上见高低，争个明白，不容许搪塞。但其实时间在我们这边，“只争朝夕”，我们也没有那么急。","index":64,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"6db91328d0","type":"paragraph","text":"根据中央文献出版社一九九六年出版的","index":65,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"73ec3d79d0","type":"paragraph","text":"这句是指：在北伐以前，军阀统治，中国的命运究竟由哪一个阶级做主？","index":2,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"756025b687","type":"paragraph","text":"“红霞”，指帝子衣服。","index":48,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"75b9d77a65","type":"paragraph","text":"十三、“泪飞顿作倾盆雨”。","index":25,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"7a5b23e8d8","type":"paragraph","text":"“旌旗”和“鼓角”都是指我军。黄洋界很陡，阵地在山腰，指挥在山头，敌人仰攻。山下并没有都被敌人占领，没有严重到这个程度。“旌旗在望”，其实没有飘扬的旗子，都是卷起的。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"7e22b2fc62","type":"paragraph","text":"二十二、《七律·答友人》的“友人”指谁？","index":43,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"820f0f8636","type":"paragraph","text":"指军阀的黄粱梦。","index":8,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"826d1e7c82","type":"paragraph","text":"十一、“天若有情天亦老”。","index":21,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"85cf25ba11","type":"paragraph","text":"“飞鸣镝”指我们的进攻。“正西风落叶下长安”，虫子怕秋冬。形势变得很快，那时是“百丈冰”，而现在正是“四海翻腾云水怒，五洲震荡风雷激”了。从去年起，我们进攻，九月开始写文章，一评苏共中央的公开信。","index":62,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"8bff0b03c6","type":"paragraph","text":"十四、“坐地日行八万里，巡天遥看一千河。”","index":27,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"8ccdf8036b","type":"paragraph","text":"郭沫若原诗针对唐僧。应针对白骨精。唐僧是不觉悟的人，被欺骗了。我的和诗是驳郭老的。","index":58,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"8e19bbecda","type":"paragraph","text":"“白烟”为水。","index":40,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"937e03e1f3","type":"paragraph","text":"二十八、“暮色苍茫看劲松，乱云飞渡仍从容。”","index":55,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"99b1be858c","type":"paragraph","text":"四、“一枕黄粱再现”。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"9ad26aaaf1","type":"paragraph","text":"十七、“别梦依稀咒逝川，故园三十二年前。⋯⋯黑手高悬霸主鞭。”","index":33,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"9e6e528f82","type":"paragraph","text":"“洞庭波”，取自《楚辞》中的《九歌·湘夫人》：“洞庭波兮木叶下”。","index":50,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"9ed9bae61a","type":"paragraph","text":"“长岛”即水陆洲，也叫橘子洲，长沙因此得名，就像汉口因在汉水之口而得名一样。","index":52,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"9f1b329489","type":"paragraph","text":"十五、“牛郎欲问瘟神事”。","index":29,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"a188a9a595","type":"paragraph","text":"八、“离天三尺三”。","index":15,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"a81962d0d8","type":"paragraph","text":"二十、“浪下三吴起白烟”。","index":39,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"ae69f48b3f","type":"paragraph","text":"这是借用李贺的句子。与人间比，天是不老的。其实天也有发生、发展、衰亡。天是自然界，包括有机界，如细菌、动物。自然界、人类社会，一样有发生和灭亡的过程。社会上的阶级，有兴起，有灭亡。","index":22,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"b2423c0596","type":"paragraph","text":"是指高兴得掉泪。","index":26,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"bab7f66333","type":"paragraph","text":"这是湖南常德的民谣。","index":16,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"bbeefcc806","type":"paragraph","text":"二、“到中流击水”。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"c1567a344b","type":"paragraph","text":"十六、“红雨随心翻作浪，青山着意化为桥。”","index":31,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"c4b0fdeda1","type":"paragraph","text":"七、“莫道君行早”。","index":13,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"ca157d4087","type":"paragraph","text":"十、“五岭逶迤腾细浪，乌蒙磅礴走泥丸。”","index":19,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"d151237aef","type":"paragraph","text":"“九嶷山”，即苍梧山，在湖南省南部。","index":46,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"dc32613c12","type":"paragraph","text":"“枯木朽株”，不是指敌方，是指自己这边，草木也可帮我们忙。“枪林逼”也是指自己这边。“枪林逼，飞将军自重霄入”是倒装笔法，就是：“飞将军自重霄入，枪林逼。”","index":12,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"dde8d97403","type":"paragraph","text":"“咒逝川”、“三十二年前”，指大革命失败，反动派镇压了革命。这里的“霸主”，就是指蒋介石。","index":34,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"de6d586ce8","type":"paragraph","text":"人坐在地球这颗行星上，不要买票，在宇宙里旅行。地球自转的里数，就是人旅行的里数。地球直径为一万二千七百多公里，乘以圆周率，即赤道长，约四万公里，再折合成华里，约八万里。人在二十四小时内走了八万里。","index":28,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"de9974c0f6","type":"paragraph","text":"一、“怅寥廓，问苍茫大地，谁主沉浮？”","index":1,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"e0a8a61872","type":"paragraph","text":"“芙蓉国”，指湖南，见谭用之诗“秋风万里芙蓉国”。“芙蓉”是指木芙蓉，不是水芙蓉，水芙蓉是荷花。谭诗可查《全唐诗》。","index":54,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"e7df3b1951","type":"paragraph","text":"二十四、“红霞万朵百重衣”。","index":47,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"e8993ba7bf","type":"paragraph","text":"“冷眼向洋”就是“横眉冷对”。","index":36,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"e974acb964","type":"paragraph","text":"十二、“一片汪洋都不见，知向谁边？”","index":23,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"ec509c2b2e","type":"paragraph","text":"“友人”指周世钊。","index":44,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"efb0cdf8ae","type":"paragraph","text":"把山比作“细浪”、“泥丸”，是“等闲”之意。","index":20,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"f627f8e286","type":"paragraph","text":"九、“西风烈，长空雁叫霜晨月。⋯⋯雄关漫道真如铁，而今迈步从头越。”","index":17,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"f8b8ca0bcd","type":"paragraph","text":"这首词上下两阕不是分写两次攻打娄山关，而是写一次。这里北有大巴山，长江、乌江之间也有山脉挡风，所以一二月也不太冷。“雁叫”、“霜晨”，是写当时景象。云贵地区就是这样，昆明更是四季如春。遵义会议后，红军北上，准备过长江，但是遇到强大阻力。为了甩开敌军，出敌不意，杀回马枪，红军又回头走，决心回遵义，结果第二次打下了娄山关，重占遵义。过娄山关时，太阳还没有落山。","index":18,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"fb79db5c60","type":"paragraph","text":"三十一、“正西风落叶下长安，飞鸣镝。”","index":61,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"},{"id":"fd44cf88cf","type":"paragraph","text":"二十九、“僧是愚氓犹可训，妖为鬼蜮必成灾。”","index":57,"publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee"}],"page":{"id":"8a65f3b238","publicationId":"wenji8","articleId":"250157bdee","start":375,"end":379}}}},"__N_SSG":true}